        <p> In between, I reserved two tickets for the fortress that we want to visit in peace tomorrow. As the day slowly turned to evening, we retreated into the car to watch another film and end the day comfortably. It was one of those relaxed days when you don't do much, but still feel like you're enjoying a little break from everyday life. And the best part: Tomorrow we'll continue with a visit to the fortress - we're curious to see what awaits us there. </p>
